Text: Seed people, seed. Don't be greedy.

This is based on my viewing of the sample, I'll correct this if the full file isn't up to par (though at present I have no reason to suspect this)

A: A perfect 10/10. 6 channels of AC-3 goodness: front left, center, right - Side left, right and LFE (low frequency effects). No sync issues either.

V: 9/10. Very slightly noticeable artifacting can give a not quite crisp look to some objects, though that could easily be the source material. I've seen worse video on original blu-rays simply down to the original cameras not dealing with variable lighting as well as standard film cameras could.
Just checked the main file and those quality ratings stand. Nice job neonrainbow :)

A very good BRRip.
A 10
V 10
